---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Contact & Feedback"
  description="Get in touch with the CTAI project. Share feedback, report issues, or request features."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-ink-200 mb-2">Contact & Feedback</h1>
    <p class="text-ink-500 text-sm mb-10">Have a suggestion, found a bug, or just want to say hello?</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-ink-300 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-display text-ink-200 mb-3">About This Project</h2>
        <p>
          CTAI (Committee Translation AI) is a personal, non-official project by Chad Jones. It is not
          affiliated with or endorsed by any Baha&rsquo;i institution. The site explores how AI tools can assist
          in the scholarly study of Shoghi Effendi&rsquo;s translations of Arabic and Persian sacred texts.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-display text-ink-200 mb-3">Get in Touch</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
          The best way to reach me is by email. I welcome feedback on the alignment quality, feature
          suggestions, bug reports, or corrections to the linguistic data.
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:chadananda@gmail.com"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-gold-400/10 hover:bg-gold-400/20 border border-gold-400/30 hover:border-gold-400/50 text-gold-400 font-mono text-sm tracking-wide rounded-md transition-all"
        >
          chadananda@gmail.com
        </a>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-display text-ink-200 mb-3">Open Source</h2>
        <p>
          This project&rsquo;s source code is available on
          <a href="https://github.com/chadananda/ctai" class="text-gold-400 hover:text-gold-300 transition-colors">GitHub</a>.
          Pull requests and issues are welcome.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
